item.title: About
item.description: I'm a San Francisco Bay Area native. I grew up in Palo Alto, went to school at Stanford to study Computer Science and now live in SF. By Day I'm a problem solver. Usually this means working with others to build things using computers. I've been a professional software engineer since 2007, a product manager since 2013, and an entrepreneur since 2014. I may be the most passionate person you'll ever work with.
